### ==================== ADMIN ENDPOINTS ====================

### 1. Create Game (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Epic Bonus Hunt #1",
  "description": "100 bonuses on Gates of Olympus - Can you guess the final balance?",
  "startingBalance": 1000.00,
  "numberOfBonuses": 100,
  "breakEvenMultiplier": 0.96,
  "pointsReward": 500
}

### 2. Get All Games (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Get All Games with Status Filter (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin?status=DRAFT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Open Guessing (Admin)
# Replace :id with actual game ID from create response
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/open
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Get All Guesses for a Game (Admin)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/guesses
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Close Guessing (Admin)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/close
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Complete Game - Draw Winner (Admin)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/complete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "finalBalance": 1250.50
}

### 8. Delete Game (Admin)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==================== USER ENDPOINTS ====================

### 9. Get Active Games (User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 10. Get Active Games (Public - No Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance

### 11. Get Game Details (User)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 12. Submit Guess (User)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/guess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "guessAmount": 1200.00
}

### 13. Update Guess (User - Same endpoint, will upsert)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/guess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "guessAmount": 1300.00
}

### 14. Get My Guess (User)
# Replace :id with actual game ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/my-guess
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 15. Get Completed Games (User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/completed
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 16. Get Completed Games (Public - No Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/completed

### ==================== ERROR CASES ====================

### 17. Submit Guess - Game Not Open (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/guess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "guessAmount": 1500.00
}

### 18. Submit Guess - Invalid Amount (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/guess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "guessAmount": -100.00
}

### 19. Submit Guess - Missing Amount (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/1/guess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
}

### 20. Open Guessing - Not Admin (Should Fail)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/open
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 21. Complete Game - Missing Final Balance (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/admin/1/complete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
}

### 22. Get Game Details - Invalid ID (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guess-the-balance/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ==================== COMPLETE WORKFLOW TEST ====================

### WORKFLOW: Complete Game Flow
# 1. Admin creates game (use request #1)
# 2. Admin opens guessing (use request #4)
# 3. User 1 submits guess (use request #12)
# 4. User 2 submits guess (change token and use request #12)
# 5. User 1 updates guess (use request #13)
# 6. Admin views all guesses (use request #5)
# 7. Admin closes guessing (use request #6)
# 8. User tries to guess (should fail - use request #17)
# 9. Admin completes game (use request #7)
# 10. Users view completed games (use request #15)

### ==================== NOTES ====================
# 
# To get tokens:
# 1. Start the backend server: npm run dev
# 2. Login via Discord OAuth in the frontend
# 3. Check browser DevTools > Application > Local Storage
# 4. Copy the token value
# 5. Replace {{adminToken}} and {{userToken}} above
#
# Admin Token: User must be in ADMIN_DISCORD_IDS env variable
# User Token: Any authenticated user
#
# Test Order:
# 1. Create game (#1)
# 2. Open guessing (#4)
# 3. Submit guesses (#12, #13)
# 4. View guesses (#5)
# 5. Close guessing (#6)
# 6. Complete game (#7)
# 7. View completed (#15)
#
